================================================================================
Depencies
================================================================================

* SDL2      (http://libsdl.org)
* SDL2_ttf  (http://libsdl.org/projects/SDL2_ttf)


================================================================================
Building the library
================================================================================

For more information, see 'README-cmake' and 'README-configure'. If you unsure
which build system to use, prefer CMake.

* Windows   :  Use CMake
* Cygwin    :  Use CMake or configure
* Linux     :  Use CMake or configure
* Mac OS X  :  Use CMake or configure
* Android   :  See README-android
* iOS       :  See README-ios


================================================================================
Linking to SDLU
================================================================================

To compile an application that uses the SDL utility library, you can use
'pkg-config', or sdlu-config:

    $ gcc program.c -o program `pkg-config --libs --cflags sdlu` [flags]
    $ gcc program.c -o program `sdlu-config --libs --cflags` [flags]


